videos.description: Brittain Brown takes the hand off and scampers up the middle for the 12-yard TD to put Duke up 10-0 in the 2nd quarter.
videos.headline: Duke RB scores from 12 yards out

videos.description: Daniel Jones finds Aaron Young for 61 yards down to the Army 1 leading to a Jones rushing TD.
videos.headline: Duke QB unleashes throw for 61 yards

videos.description: Kelvin Hopkins Jr. keeps it and scores to get Army on the board 17-7 in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Army QB scores the 10-yard TD

videos.description: Deon Jackson takes the hand off and is able to fight his way into the end zone extending Duke's lead to 24-7.
videos.headline: Duke RB breaks multiple tackles and scores TD

videos.description: Camden Harrison gets behind Duke's defense and scores the easy touchdown cutting the Blue Devils' lead to 24-14.
videos.headline: Army WR gets behind defense and scores TD

videos.description: Daniel Jones finds Aaron Young for 25 yards extending Duke's lead to 31-14.
